quran[11{c,v,t}:
20,77,aur hum ne moose ki taraf wahi bhaije ke hamaray bundon ko raton raat nikaal le jao phir un ke liye darya mein ( laathi maar kar ) khushk rasta bana do phir tum ko nah to ( firaon ke ) aa pakranay ka khauf hoga aur nah ( ghark honay ka ) dar
20,78,phir firaon ne apne lashkar ke sath un ka taqubkiya to darya ( ki moajoon ) ne un par charh kar inhen dhaank liya ( yani duubo diya )
20,79,aur firaon ne apni qoum ko gumraah kardiya aur seedhay raste par nah dala
20,80,ae all Yaqoob hum ne tum ko tumahray dushman se nijaat di aur torat dainay ke liye tum se koh tor ki dahni taraf muqarrar ki aur tum par mann aur salwa nazilkiya
20,81,( aur hukum diya ke ) jo pakeeza cheeze hum ne tum ko di hain un ko khao. aur is mein hadd se nah niklana. warna tum par mera ghazab nazil hoga. aur jis par mera ghazab nazil howa woh halaak hogaya
20,82,aur jo tauba kere aur imaan laaye aur amal naik kere phir seedhay raste chalay is ko mein bakhash dainay wala hon
20,83,aur ae moose tum ne apni qoum se ( agay chalay anay mein ) kyun jaldi ki
20,84,kaha woh mere peechay ( aa rahay ) hain aur ae perwar-digaar mein ne teri taraf ( anay ki ) jaldi is liye ki ke to khush ho
20,85,farmaya ke hum ne tumhari qoum ko tumahray baad azmaish mein daal diya hai aur samri ne un ko b_hka diya hai
20,86,aur moose ghsse aur gham ki haalat mein apni qoum ke paas wapas aeye ( aur ) kehnay lagey ke ae qoumkiya tumahray perwar-digaar ne tum se aik acha wada nahikiya tha?kiya ( meri judai ki ) muddat tumhe daraaz ( maloom ) hui ya tum ne chaha ke tum par tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se ghazab nazil ho. aur ( is liye ) tum ne mujh se jo wadakiya tha ( is ke ) khilaafkiya
20,87,woh kehnay lagey ke hum ne apne ikhtiyar se tum se wada khilaaf nahikiya. balkay hum logon ke زیوروں ka boojh uthaye hue they. phir hum ne is ko ( aag mein ) daal diya aur isi terhan samri ne daal diya
